okay?

50:09.720 --> 50:11.011
I don't want
to make a mistake.

50:11.011 --> 50:13.929
Then keep your fucking
mouth shut.

50:13.929 --> 50:16.053
There's nothing in there
to connect you to Tommy?

50:16.053 --> 50:17.720
Not enough for a subpoena.

50:20.303 --> 50:21.929
[taps table]

50:21.929 --> 50:24.720
That job up in Revere
with the guards,

50:24.720 --> 50:27.053
is that...
is that clean?

50:27.053 --> 50:28.887
I took care of it.

50:28.887 --> 50:30.553
What'd you do
with the guns after?

50:30.553 --> 50:32.428
I took care of it.

50:32.428 --> 50:33.929
Okay.

50:33.929 --> 50:35.720
Hey, I just want to help.

50:35.720 --> 50:37.679
You want to help?
You can take care of yourself.

50:37.679 --> 50:39.011
-You understand?
-Yeah. Yeah.

50:39.011 --> 50:40.387
You stay on your meds,
no more Florida.

50:40.387 --> 50:42.428
-Okay, great.
-[door slams]

50:42.428 --> 50:44.303
You here
for the thing?

50:44.303 --> 50:46.845
Yeah.

50:46.845 --> 50:48.845
What's the fucking smoke
doing here?

50:48.845 --> 50:50.220
Why do we come to Hook?

50:50.220 --> 50:51.470
Fucking drugs.

50:52.804 --> 50:54.220
And guns.

51:08.762 --> 51:10.720
[Sheehan] Stop asking me
the same question.

51:10.720 --> 51:12.720
I don't know anything about
what happened to Kinicki

51:12.720 --> 51:14.095
when he disappeared.

51:14.095 --> 51:15.387
But you do know
that he was trying

51:15.387 --> 51:16.887
to turn his life around,
don't you?

51:16.887 --> 51:18.261
Aren't we all?

51:23.428 --> 51:26.095
♪ dramatic music plays ♪

51:30.970 --> 51:32.261
Okay.

51:35.261 --> 51:37.011
So, ahem,

51:37.011 --> 51:38.595
why don't you tell us
about the armored car

51:38.595 --> 51:40.303
that went missing
in Revere Beach, hmm?

51:49.887 --> 51:51.178
Oh, okay.

51:51.178 --> 51:53.845
So, have you heard
of a cultural phenomenon

51:53.845 --> 51:56.261
called "code of silence"?

51:56.261 --> 51:58.970
It's a monolithic belief.
Don't talk to cops.

51:58.970 --> 52:01.136
This includes
prosecutors.

52:01.136 --> 52:04.095
What's this Revere Beach thing
you mentioned?

52:06.345 --> 52:09.762
Well, it's a string
of armed car robberies

52:09.762 --> 52:11.220
that have plagued Boston,

52:11.220 --> 52:12.637
one of which involved
the disappearance

52:12.637 --> 52:14.470
of three guards
in Revere Beach.

52:14.470 --> 52:17.178
Now, the armored truck
that was hijacked

52:17.178 --> 52:18.428
was recovered
out of the Lynn Marsh.

52:18.428 --> 52:21.762
The robberies are believed
to be the work

52:21.762 --> 52:23.970
of a small group of individuals
who live in Charlestown.

52:25.887 --> 52:27.637
So, what do you know
about that?

52:27.637 --> 52:30.345
Saw something
on the local news.

52:35.762 --> 52:38.053
Did you disobey orders?

52:38.053 --> 52:41.220
Drank a little too much
the night before.

52:41.220 --> 52:44.929
A little cocaine to get yourself
ready for the job?

52:46.220 --> 52:47.679
Is that why
things went wrong?

52:47.679 --> 52:49.387
Drinking and drugging?

52:49.387 --> 52:51.470
You're talking bullshit.

52:51.470 --> 52:53.762
-Is that why you slap your wife?
-You black bastard.

52:53.762 --> 52:55.637
Domestic dispute's
in the file--

52:55.637 --> 52:56.720
Gorilla!

52:56.720 --> 52:58.011
[jurors gasp]

52:59.095 --> 53:00.887
[Sheehan]
Gorilla!

53:00.887 --> 53:03.845
Gorilla? I'm King Kong!

53:03.845 --> 53:06.053
I'm going to fucking bury you,
you fucking nigger!

53:13.804 --> 53:15.220
[inhales deeply]

53:26.303 --> 53:28.804
Hey, did you hear what happened
in court today?

53:28.804 --> 53:30.387
-[Frankie] Nope.
-[kids laughing]

53:30.387 --> 53:32.595
Court reporter comes in,
getting her perm done.

53:32.595 --> 53:34.929
She starts talking
about Sheik.

53:34.929 --> 53:36.970
He attacked
the prosecutor.

53:36.970 --> 53:38.470
He got arrested.

53:39.970 --> 53:41.261
Fuck.

53:41.261 --> 53:43.136
[cartoonish music
playing on TV]

53:43.136 --> 53:44.512
You gotta be
kidding me.

53:44.512 --> 53:46.178
No.

53:46.178 --> 53:47.845
What the fuck
am I supposed to do?

53:47.845 --> 53:50.929
Look, it's all right.
He hasn't said anything yet,

53:50.929 --> 53:52.220
and so we just...

53:52.220 --> 53:53.929
we gotta handle it
on our end.

53:53.929 --> 53:55.970
He's going to be worried
about his kids.

53:55.970 --> 53:57.929
-[Cathy] Yup.
-[Frankie] Like I'd be.

53:57.929 --> 54:00.095
That's why I'm going to go over,
I'm going to go see Tara,

54:00.095 --> 54:01.845
going to put some cash
in her hand.

54:01.845 --> 54:03.095
-Hey.
-Yeah?

54:03.095 --> 54:04.762
I'm going to put
cash in her hand.

54:04.762 --> 54:06.804
I'm going to let her know
she doesn't gotta worry

54:06.804 --> 54:08.345
about rent,
food, nothing.

54:08.345 --> 54:09.929
As soon as Sheik calls her

54:09.929 --> 54:11.762
and hears that everything's
been taken care of,

54:11.762 --> 54:13.428
he'll play the part.

54:13.428 --> 54:15.345
That's a good plan.

54:17.011 --> 54:18.553
Meat loaf's ready
in five.

54:18.553 --> 54:20.261
These guys are all
in pajamas,

54:20.261 --> 54:22.178
but Kick's got a poem
she's gotta write for school.

54:22.178 --> 54:23.512
I'll be right back.

54:25.428 --> 54:27.303
We're good.
We got this.

54:29.887 --> 54:31.428
-I love you.
-I love you.

54:34.637 --> 54:36.261
Five minutes
on that meat loaf.

54:36.261 --> 54:38.178
Please don't let it burn,
all right?

54:38.178 --> 54:40.470
[cartoonish music
playing on TV continues]

54:40.470 --> 54:43.053
[door squeaks open]

54:43.053 --> 54:46.095
King Kong!
King fuckin' Kong!

54:46.095 --> 54:49.136
Sheehan was just mad
he didn't think about it first.

54:49.136 --> 54:51.261
You know Kong dies
at the end, right?

54:51.261 --> 54:52.970
[laughs]

54:54.387 --> 54:56.178
Hey, counselor,
might I remind you

54:56.178 --> 54:58.345
that bringing up the dead guards
is a no-no.

54:58.345 --> 55:00.553
You can lead the jury
to the Revere heist,

55:00.553 --> 55:02.136
you can't tell them.

55:02.136 --> 55:04.178
Hey, Sheehan's sitting
in a cell, all right?

55:04.178 --> 55:05.804
A few days, he'll flip.

55:05.804 --> 55:07.595
[Eloise] God, did you ever
feel like your life

55:07.595 --> 55:09.845
was just one big
fucking chest wound?

55:09.845 --> 55:11.679
Every day,
and twice on Sunday.

55:11.679 --> 55:13.428
[Eloise]
You're my chest wound, pal.

55:13.428 --> 55:15.512
The DA finds out that you broke
the chain of evidence,

55:15.512 --> 55:17.762
we say goodbye to our badges
and our pensions.

55:17.762 --> 55:21.303
Did anyone ever tell you
that you look like Sophia Lauren

55:21.303 --> 55:23.345
when you get mad?

55:23.345 --> 55:25.762
[cell phone rings]

55:25.762 --> 55:27.512
[laughs]
Oh.

55:28.929 --> 55:30.553
There it is.

55:30.553 --> 55:32.345
Knock yourself out.

55:32.345 --> 55:34.470
-You...
-Yeah.

55:34.470 --> 55:36.679
[cell phone ringing]

55:37.970 --> 55:39.095
[clears throat]

55:41.804 --> 55:43.553
Benner.

55:43.553 --> 55:45.011
No, he's in the john.

55:45.011 --> 55:46.512
Told me to find out
what you got.

55:50.720 --> 55:52.053
Yes, thank you.

55:55.136 --> 55:56.762
FBI traced the fragment.

55:56.762 --> 55:57.720
And?

55:59.011 --> 56:00.553
An AK-47.

56:01.887 --> 56:03.345
Fuck, yeah.

56:03.345 --> 56:05.011
Let's go to work.

56:05.011 --> 56:07.178
You see that look?
That look right there?

56:07.178 --> 56:08.845
I love that look.

56:08.845 --> 56:11.553
That's the look that says
that I was right.

56:11.553 --> 56:13.053
Fuck you.

56:13.053 --> 56:14.387
[Jackie]
Oh, you find that gun,

56:14.387 --> 56:17.887
and I'm going
to make your legs shake.

56:17.887 --> 56:19.178
I find that gun, asshole,

56:19.178 --> 56:20.845
you better sleep
with one eye cracked.

